summary:
Customer service specialist with experience in supply chain process from quotes to post delivery is open for a global assignment. I have been coordinating projects with worldwide companies in countries such as Iran, Congo, Europe, Brazil, and others. I speak and write fluent Dutch, English, French, Spanish and Swedish.
I have all the necessary documents and certificates to execute my work.
